    "Thus, allowing users to choose their visualizations can provide a more flexible analysis.Stage3: Task decomposition.",
    "We design the decomposition following a \"on-demand\" strategy.",
    "In other words, execution is prioritized, and decomposition is considered only if the task is not completed.",
    "This approach aims to ensure users can see initial results quickly in an interactive environment.",
